In the first half of the show, author, economist and talk radio host Andre Eggelletion discusses some of the surprising recent moves of the Fed and what it means to the global economy, foreign policy and ultimately the average US citizen.

During the latter half of the program, expert in theology, biblical languages, and world civilizations, Mike Heiser, talked about his work on ancient astronauts, Nazi UFOs, giants in history, as well as end times and the New World Order. He also addressed the question of whether conservative Judaism and Christianity could sustain a genuine ET disclosure.
